Dependances
===========
QATools require [eZ Components](http://ezcomponents.org/). You can:

* [Install eZ Components](http://ezcomponents.org/docs/install) before using QAtools,
* Download eZ Components and put the components in the lib/ezc directory.

If you want to check twig and/or yml files you need to install composer.
And run "composer install" or "composer update" at the top of the application